---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const schema = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "Person",
  "name": "Stephan Schmied",
  "jobTitle": "Hair & Make-up Artist",
  "description": "Hair & Make-up Artist in Berlin seit 1987. Spezialist für Bridal, Editorial und Events.",
  "url": "https://stephanschmied.com",
  "address": { "@type": "PostalAddress", "addressLocality": "Berlin", "addressCountry": "DE" },
  "sameAs": ["https://instagram.com/schmiedsteph"],
  "knowsAbout": ["Hair Styling", "Make-up Artistry", "Bridal Make-up", "Editorial Make-up"]
};
---

<Layout
  title="Stephan Schmied – Hair & Make-up Artist Berlin"
  description="Hair & Make-up Artist in Berlin seit 1987. Spezialist für Bridal, Editorial, Events und Beauty Workshops. Brand Ambassador Max Factor 2007–2019."
  schemaOrg={schema}
>
  <!-- ═══ HERO ═══ -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-bg">
      <img
        src="https://placehold.co/1920x1080/F5F0EB/C9A96E?text=Hero+Bild"
        alt="Stephan Schmied bei der Arbeit"
        width="1920" height="1080"
        loading="eager"
        fetchpriority="high"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
    <div class="hero-content container">
      <p class="hero-label">Hair &amp; Make-up Artist</p>
      <h1 class="hero-title">Stephan<br>Schmied</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">Hair &amp; Make-up Artist · Berlin · Since 1987</p>
      <a href="/portfolio" class="btn btn-gold">Arbeiten entdecken</a>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-scroll-hint" aria-hidden="true">
      <span></span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ LOGO BAR ═══ -->
  <section class="logo-bar">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="label text-center" style="display:block">Vertrauen von</span>
      <div class="logo-grid">
        <span class="logo-item">Max Factor</span>
        <span class="logo-item">Douglas</span>
        <span class="logo-item">Gala</span>
        <span class="logo-item">GQ</span>
        <span class="logo-item">Interview Magazine</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ CELEBRITY INTRO ═══ -->
  <section class="section celeb-intro">
    <div class="container celeb-grid fade-in">
      <div class="celeb-portrait-wrap">
        <img
          src="/images/stephan-portrait.jpg"
          alt="Stephan Schmied – Hair & Make-up Artist"
          width="480" height="600"
          loading="lazy"
          class="celeb-portrait"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="celeb-content">
        <span class="label">Von den Covern der Welt zu deinem besonderen Moment</span>
        <div class="celeb-names">
          <span class="celeb-name">Kate Moss</span>
          <span class="celeb-name">Iris Berben</span>
          <span class="celeb-name">Gwyneth Paltrow</span>
          <span class="celeb-name">Franziska Knuppe</span>
          <span class="celeb-name">Liv Tyler</span>
          <span class="celeb-name">Herbert Grönemeyer</span>
          <span class="celeb-name">Eva Padberg</span>
          <span class="celeb-name">Katja Riemann</span>
        </div>
        <div class="celeb-text">
          <p>In fast vier Jahrzehnten hatte ich das Privileg, einige der bekanntesten Gesichter der Welt zu stylen – auf Laufstegen, für Kampagnen und auf den Covern internationaler Magazine.</p>
          <p class="mt-sm">Und jetzt? Jetzt bringe ich genau diese Erfahrung zu dir. Denn du verdienst den gleichen Standard – ob für deine Hochzeit, dein Event oder deinen Beauty Workshop. Echte Hände. Echtes Handwerk. Kein Filter.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ ABOUT PREVIEW ═══ -->
  <section class="section about-preview">
    <div class="container about-grid">
      <div class="about-img-wrap fade-in">
        <img
          src="/images/stephan-portrait.jpg"
          alt="Portrait Stephan Schmied"
          width="480" height="480"
          loading="lazy"
          class="about-portrait"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="about-text fade-in delay-1">
        <span class="label">Über mich</span>
        <h2>Fast 40 Jahre<br>Erfahrung</h2>
        <div class="divider"></div>
        <p>Vom Wiener Friseursalon über internationale Fashion Weeks bis zu den größten Beauty-Magazinen Deutschlands. Mein Talent: die individuelle Schönheit jedes Menschen hervorzuheben.</p>
        <p class="mt-sm">Echte Hände. Echtes Handwerk. In einer Welt voller Filter und KI-generierter Perfektion – ein Artist, der dich wirklich schön macht.</p>
        <a href="/about" class="btn btn-outline mt-md">Mehr über mich</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ SERVICES ═══ -->
  <section class="section services-section" style="background:#fff">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center fade-in">
        <span class="label">Was ich anbiete</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Services</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="services-grid mt-md">
        <a href="/services#bridal" class="service-card fade-in">
          <div class="service-card-img-wrap">
            <img src="https://placehold.co/600x400/1A1A1A/FAFAF8?text=Bridal" alt="Bridal Make-up" width="600" height="400" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="service-card-body">
            <h3>Bridal</h3>
            <p>Dein perfekter Look für den wichtigsten Tag. Vom Probetermin bis zum letzten Tanz.</p>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/services#editorial" class="service-card fade-in delay-1">
          <div class="service-card-img-wrap">
            <img src="https://placehold.co/600x400/4A4A4A/FAFAF8?text=Editorial" alt="Editorial Make-up" width="600" height="400" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="service-card-body">
            <h3>Events &amp; Editorial</h3>
            <p>Fashion, Beauty, Celebrity. Für Shootings, Kampagnen und Red Carpet.</p>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/masterclasses" class="service-card fade-in delay-2">
          <div class="service-card-img-wrap">
            <img src="https://placehold.co/600x400/C9A96E/1A1A1A?text=Beauty+Workshops" alt="Beauty Workshops" width="600" height="400" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="service-card-body">
            <h3>Beauty Workshops</h3>
            <p>Du willst die Techniken lernen, mit denen ich Kate Moss und Iris Berben gestylt habe? In meinen Beauty Workshops zeige ich dir Schritt für Schritt, wie Profis arbeiten – mit Produkten, die du zu Hause oder bei DM findest.</p>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ TESTIMONIALS ═══ -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center fade-in">
        <span class="label">Stimmen meiner Kunden</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Was sie sagen</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="testimonials-grid mt-md">
        <div class="testimonial fade-in">
          <blockquote>"Stephan hat mich an meinem Hochzeitstag so wunderschön gemacht, ich habe mich wie ein Star gefühlt."</blockquote>
          <cite>— Anna K., Braut</cite>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial fade-in delay-1">
          <blockquote>"Professionell, kreativ und unglaublich einfühlsam. Die beste Entscheidung für unser Shooting."</blockquote>
          <cite>— Maria S., Fotografin</cite>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial fade-in delay-2">
          <blockquote>"Nach 40 Jahren Erfahrung merkt man jeden Pinselstrich. Absolute Weltklasse."</blockquote>
          <cite>— Thomas R., Art Director</cite>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ CTA ═══ -->
  <section class="cta-section fade-in">
    <h2>Bereit für deinen Look?</h2>
    <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-gold">Jetzt Kontakt aufnehmen</a>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* ─── Hero ─── */
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    height: 100vh;
    min-height: 600px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: #F5F0EB;
    color: #2C2825;
  }
  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 0;
  }
  .hero-bg img {
    width: 100%; height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center;
  }
  .hero-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(245,240,235,0.3) 0%, rgba(245,240,235,0.15) 60%, rgba(245,240,235,0.4) 100%);
    z-index: 1;
  }
  .hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .hero-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-gold);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    max-width: none;
  }
  .hero-title {
    font-family: var(--font-signature);
    font-size: clamp(4rem, 12vw, 10rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 0.95;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: #2C2825;
    text-transform: none;
  }
  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(44,40,37,0.6);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    max-width: none;
  }
  .hero-scroll-hint {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 2.5rem;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    z-index: 2;
  }
  .hero-scroll-hint span {
    display: block;
    width: 1px;
    height: 60px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, rgba(44,40,37,0.35));
    margin: 0 auto;
    animation: scrollHint 2s ease infinite;
  }
  @keyframes scrollHint {
    0%   { transform: scaleY(0); transform-origin: top; }
    50%  { transform: scaleY(1); transform-origin: top; }
    51%  { transform: scaleY(1); transform-origin: bottom; }
    100% { transform: scaleY(0); transform-origin: bottom; }
  }

  /* ─── Celebrity Intro ─── */
  .celeb-intro { background: var(--color-bg); }
  .celeb-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 380px 1fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .celeb-portrait-wrap { flex-shrink: 0; }
  .celeb-portrait {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: top;
    border-radius: 4px;
    filter: none;
  }
  .celeb-names {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
    margin: 1.5rem 0 2rem;
  }
  .celeb-name {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 22px;
    color: #2C2825;
    line-height: 1.5;
    text-transform: none;
    letter-spacing: 0;
  }
  .celeb-text p {
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    max-width: 52ch;
  }
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .celeb-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: var(--sp-md); }
    .celeb-portrait { max-width: 300px; border-radius: 50%; aspect-ratio: 1; object-fit: cover; }
    .celeb-names { flex-direction: row; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0 1.5rem; }
  }

  /* ─── About preview ─── */
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.2fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .about-portrait {
    border-radius: 50%;
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    object-fit: cover;
    border: 3px solid var(--color-border);
  }
  .about-text h2 { font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem); }

  /* ─── Services ─── */
  .services-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  .service-card {
    display: block;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: box-shadow var(--transition);
  }
  .service-card:hover { box-shadow: 0 8px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
  .service-card-img-wrap { overflow: hidden; }
  .service-card img {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 4/3;
    object-fit: cover;
    transition: transform 0.45s ease;
  }
  .service-card:hover img { transform: scale(1.04); }
  .service-card-body { padding: 1.5rem; }
  .service-card-body h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .service-card-body p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    max-width: none;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .services-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: var(--sp-md); }
    .about-portrait { max-width: 260px; margin: 0 auto; }
  }

</style>
